```dockerfile
# Stage 1: Build frontend
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /app/frontend

COPY frontend/package*.json ./

RUN npm ci

COPY frontend/ ./

RUN npm run build

# Stage 2: Build Python dependencies
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    build-essential \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN pip install --upgrade pip && pip install poetry

WORKDIR /app

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-dev --no-interaction --no-ansi

# Stage 3: Runtime
FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Analytics Platform Team" \
      description="Production-grade analytics platform with Flask backend and React frontend"

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq5 \
    unixodbc \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Create non-root user
RUN useradd -m -u 1000 superset

WORKDIR /app

# Copy frontend assets
COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist/ /app/static/

# Copy Python virtualenv from builder
COPY --from=python-builder /app/.venv /app/.venv

# Copy application code
COPY --chown=superset:superset . .

# Activate virtualenv in PATH
ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH" \
    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 \
    PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1

USER superset

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
